column1: The Plant List includes 108,003 scientific plant names of species rank for the family Compositae. Of these 32,913 are accepted species names.

The Plant List includes a further 32,205 scientific plant names of infraspecific rank for the family Compositae. We do not intend The Plant List to be complete for names of infraspecific rank. These are primarily included because names of species rank are synonyms of accepted infraspecific names.
